Waveroom Server

an alternative waveroom server

Built to stream my music library to the Waveroom Blackberry Application (http://www.waveroomapp.com/) from my home linux box

requires Sinatra/Ruby. thin is my webserver of choice, not yet tested with mongrel or unicorn

INSTALLATION:

bundle install
cp waveroom-example.yml waveroom.yml
[edit waveroom.yml with your music paths]
thin start -C config.yml

